    <item>
      <title>匈牙利与中国签署 10 亿欧元贷款协议，寻求融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/hungary-embraces-chinese-loan-financing-after-1-billion-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利表示，今年 4 月该国从中国获得了 10 亿欧元贷款，并补充称，随着与中国的经济联系不断加强，此类融资在未来可能会变得更加普遍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/hungary-embraces-chinese-loan-financing-after-1-billion-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 17:49:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多承诺减缓移民速度。加拿大央行对此表示怀疑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/trudeau-pledged-to-slow-immigration-the-bank-of-canada-has-doubts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贾斯汀·特鲁多政府何时能够以及在多大程度上减少加拿大临时居民的数量存在越来越大的不确定性，这给财政和货币政策制定者的一个关键输入带来了混乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/trudeau-pledged-to-slow-immigration-the-bank-of-canada-has-doubts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 17:45:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
